text: Wiþ heafodece & wiþ ealdum heafodece & wiþ healfes heafdes ece.

Wiþ aswollenum eagum & god eah sealf & wið miste on eagan & wið flie & wið wyrmum on eagum & wiþ þæm gif flæsc on eagum weaxe & gis on eagum weaxan reade sponge & gif eagan tyren & sceade sealf to eagum & smeþe eah sealf.
Wiþ earwærce & wiþ þæm gif wyrmas syn on earan & god ear sealf.
Wiþ toþece & gif teþ syn hole.
Wiþ innan tobrocenum muðe.
Wiþ ceocadle & wiþ ceolwærce.
Wiþ heals wærce.
Wiþ bite.
Wiþ hwostan.
Wiþ þam þe mon blode hræce.
Wiþ seondum geallan.
Wiþ þære geolwan adle.
Wiþ breost wærce.
Wiþ hwostan & wiþ lungenadle.
Wiþ magan wærce & wiþ aþundenesse.
Wið milt wærce.
Wiþ linden wærce.
Wiþ wambe wærce & rysel wærce.
Wiþ blædder wærce.
Wiþ þam gif man ne mæge gemigan & þam men þe stanas weaxan on þære blædran.
Wiþ þam gif men sie se utgang forseten.
Wiþ utsihtadle drenc & briw.
Wiþ þam wyrmum þe beoþ on mannes innoþe.
Wiþ lið wærce.
Wiþ weartum.
Wið þam miclan lice smiring & bæþ & drenc & briw.
Wiþ singalum þurste untrumra manna.
Wiþ innan fortoge & smælþearma ece.
Wiþ þam þe man sie mid fyre anum forbærned & wiþ þam þe man sie mid wætan forbærned & wiþ sunbryne.
Wiþ þeore drenc & eft wiþ þære & sceotendum wenne & eft beþing wiþ þam gif þeor gewunige on anre stowe.
Wiþ wenne sealf.
Wiþ dolge sealf.
Wiþ þam gif man sie ufan on heafod wund & sie ban gebrocen & wiþ þam gif sio eaxl upstige & god dolhdrenc & gif gebrocen ban sie on heafde & of nelle.
Wiþ hundes slite & wiþ þon gif sinwe forcorfene & wiþ þam gif sinwe sien gescruncene.
Wiþ gongewifran bite.
Wiþ cancre.
Wiþ þam þe wif ne mæge bearn acennan & gif of wife nelle gan æfter þam beorþre þæt gecyndelic sie & gif of wife sie dead bearn & wiþ þam gif wif blede to swiþe æfter þam beorþre.
Wiþ þam þe wifum sie forstanden hira monaðgecynd & wiþ þam gif wife to swiþe of flowe sio monoþgecynd.
Wiþ smeagea wyrme smiring & anlegen & beþing & sealf.
Wiþ þam þe man sie monaþseoc.
Wiþ ealle feondes costunga drenc & sealf, wiþ þon ilcan & hu man scyle gewitseocne man lacnian & hu mon scyle wyrcean spiwdrenc utyrnendum.
Wiþ þam gif swiþdrenc on men gesittan & he nelle utgan.
Wiþ attres drence.
Wiþ lusum.
Wiþ þam gif þorn stinge mon on fot oððe hreod & þonne nelle ofgan.
Wiþ æsmælum & wiþ eallum eagna wærce.
Wiþ lyft adle gif se muþ sie woh oþþe won læcedom & beþing & bæþ sealf & leah & blodes læs.
Wiþ ficadle drenc & beþing.
Wiþ sculdor wærce & earma.
Wiþ cneowa sare.
Wiþ fota sare.
Wiþ þam gif þu ne mæge blod dolg forwriþan.
Wiþ þam gif meoloc sie gewerd.
Wiþ nihtgengean sealf.
Wiþ þam gif men beo sio heafodpanne gehlenced.
Wið þam gif men nelle meltan his mete.
Wiþ wif gemædlan.
Wiþ feondes costunga.
Wiþ þeor wenne gif he sie men on cneowe oþþe on oþrum lime.
Be þam hu mon scyle ear sealfe wyrcean.
Wiþ ælfcynne sealf & wiþ niht gengan & þam monnum þe deofol mid hæmð.

Wiþ ælfadle læcedom & eft hu mon sceal on þa wyrte singan ær hi mon nime & eft hu mon sceal þa wyrta don under weofod & ofer singan & eft tacnu be þam hwæþer hit sie ælfsogoþa & tacn hu þu ongitan meaht hwæþer hine mon mæg gelacnian & drencas & gebedu wiþ ælcre feondes costunge.
Tacnu hu þu meaht ongitan hwæþer mon sie on wæterælfadle & læcedom wiþ þam & gealdor on to singanne & þæt ilce mon mæg singan on wunda.
Wið deofle liþe drenc & ungemynde & wiþ deofles costunga.
Wiþ þon gif mon sie gegymed & tacnu hwæþer he libban mæge.
Drenc wiþ þam gif þeor sie on men.
Wiþ deofleseoce & wiþ deofle.
Wiþ weden heorte leoht drenc.
Wiþ þam gif men sie maga asurod & forþunden & wiþ magan wærce & gif man biþ aþunden.
Wiþ wambe wærce & wiþ magan wærce & wiþ wambe heardnesse.
Wiþ springe smiring & sealf.
Wiþ attre drenc & smiring.
Wiþ þære geolwan adle.
Wiþ þam gif innelfe si ute.
Wiþ ælcre innan untrymnesse & wiþ hefignesse & wiþ hleorblæce.
Be þam hu man scyle halige sealfe wyrcean.
